<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
3. In &sect;1007.7 of the Georgia order, paragraph (e)(4); 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
4. In &sect;1011.7(d)(3) of the Tennessee Valley order, the words ``from'', ``there'', ``a greater quantity of route
disposition, except filled milk, during the month'', and ``than in this marketing area''; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
5. In &sect;1046.2 of the Louisville-Lexington-Evansville order, the word ``Pulaski''. 
