<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
promulgated by the Board, each Bank shall establish a Program to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
subsidize the interest rate on advances to members engaged in 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
lending for long-term, low- and moderate-income, owner-occupied 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
housing at subsidized interest rates. 
