<TEXT>
 
<!-- PJG STAG 4702 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Section 960.14(e)(1)(ii)(A) of the proposed rule provides that 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
during the required long-term period applicable to an 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
owner-occupied housing unit assisted by a grant provided under the 
