of sampling to monitor AHP-assisted projects. The Board 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
recognizes that as the number of AHP-assisted projects in 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
existence grows, the costs of monitoring these projects may place 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
an undue financial burden on the Banks and the AHP. Monitoring 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
AHP-assisted projects on a sample basis may be one way to minimize 
