of relevant reports or certifications obtained from the sponsor, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
including any reports or certifications received pursuant to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
&sect;960.15(c)(1)(ii) of the proposed rule and, at least on a sample 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
basis, periodic review of land title records at intervals 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
determined by the Bank, based on the amount of funds received by 
