<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 (1) Each Bank shall require an 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
applicant receiving a subsidized advance or direct subsidy 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
pursuant to this part to report at least annually to the Bank on 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the manner in which it has used the funds, with such reports 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
continuing until the funds have been fully disbursed by the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
applicant. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
