<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
_(1) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Owner-occupied housing units_
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(i) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Initial certification.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Where a subsidized advance or direct subsidy is used to finance 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the purchase of an owner-occupied housing unit, the Bank shall 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
require the sponsor to certify, at the time a household enters 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
into a purchase contract for such unit or at the closing on the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
financing for such unit, that the unit has been sold to a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
household with an income at or below the level committed to in the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
AHP application. Where a subsidized advance or direct subsidy is 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
used to finance the rehabilitation of an owner-occupied housing 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
unit, the Bank shall require the sponsor to certify at the time a 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
loan or grant is committed to fund such rehabilitation that the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
household that owns and occupies the unit has an income at or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
below the level committed to in the AHP application. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
