<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 If an owner-occupied housing 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
unit assisted by a grant provided under the AHP is not subject to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
a deed restriction or other legally enforceable mechanism 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
restricting transfer of ownership to a household with an income at 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
or below the level committed to in the AHP application, the Bank 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
shall require the sponsor to report to the Bank or its designee, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
at least annually for the required long-term period, the number of 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
any such units that are sold to households whose incomes exceed 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the level committed to in the AHP application, and to certify to 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the Bank that it is continuing to satisfy its commitment, pursuant 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
to its legally binding agreement with the Bank. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
