<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Fraud or willful non-compliance.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 (1) In the event of an 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
applicant's, sponsor's or owner's fraud with respect to the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
requirements of this part, the Bank shall exclude the applicant, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
sponsor or owner, respectively, on a permanent basis, from future 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
participation in the AHP. In the event of an applicant's, 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
sponsor's or owner's willful non-compliance with the requirements 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
of this part, the Bank shall suspend the applicant, sponsor or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
owner, respectively, at least on a temporary basis, from future 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
participation in the AHP during the period such willful 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
non-compliance continues, and may exclude such party permanently 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
from future participation in the AHP. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) In the event of an applicant's fraud or willful 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
non-compliance with respect to the requirements of this part, the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Bank shall recover from the applicant the full amount of the AHP 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
subsidy provided to the project. 
