<!-- PJG STAG 4702 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
The FHWA is proposing to remove these sections because they are duplicated by State laws and can only be enforced by
State or local agencies. In addition, the requirements for lighting devices are addressed in part 393 of the FMCSRs.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

